  "detailed_description": "Kung Fu Legend will <strong>twist your nipples</strong> while making you laugh and chuckle as you go through a <strong>funny, silly, whimsical world</strong> full of wacky characters and <strong>goofy dark humor!</strong><br>You will face many enemies in challenging battles in order to pursue your succulent wet dream of becoming a true kung fu master by collecting all the dojo belts!<br>The combat system is the shit and will leave your forehead sweatier than a kangaroo in a sauna!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"This game is hilarious!\" - some guy named Steve</h2><br><br>This game will show you the true meaning of life as you discover how fun violence is! and I take no responsibility for people becoming religious when they see the light through this wonderful experience!<br>Don't let the cute graphics fool you, this game is fucked up! and that's why you should buy it!<br><i>Allergy warning: the game contains peanuts.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Kung Fu Battles! Holy Shit!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968640/extras/3a7a74e4d4b36be5ebdcc0b29192222f.poster.avif?t=1700744880\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968640/extras/3a7a74e4d4b36be5ebdcc0b29192222f.webm?t=1700744880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968640/extras/3a7a74e4d4b36be5ebdcc0b29192222f.mp4?t=1700744880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968640/extras/58364d685ee23b80301f9552b93e201e.poster.avif?t=1700744880\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968640/extras/58364